channel.description: Marinade: 2 cups Liquid Amino 2 cups Water 2 tbsp Liquid Smoke 1/4 cup Maple Syrup 2 tsp Cumin 2 tsp Pepper 2 tsp Garlic Powder 2 tsp Smoked Paprika Marinate for 1 hour and place on parchment paper on baking sheet. Bake at 400 degrees for 25 minutes Save Marinade, good for 7 days.
